🏪 Inventory Stock Dashboard


💼 What is this project?

This dashboard tracks stock levels, inventory value, and product categories.

🎯 Purpose:

To help store managers know which products are low in stock or overstocked.

💡 Benefits:

Avoids stockouts and overstocking.
Helps maintain balanced inventory.
Gives a clear view of total stock value and category performance.

📈 Key Insights:

Total Stock Value 💰
Product Quantity by Category 📦
Reorder Alert for Low Stock ⚠️
